data.description: Your new home awaits! This 3 bed, 2.5 bath pool home has been meticulously maintained by the original owners, and is move-in ready. Open design features a spacious kitchen and upstairs loft. The fenced backyard has a pavered patio, pool (with fountain) and a beautiful pond view perfect for relaxing and entertaining. Located in desirable community just minutes to restaurants & shopping at River City Marketplace.
